issues.description: Profile "Profile1" has one or more connections configured with Use-BIOS boot settings. OneView does not support profile connections configured with a mixture of Use-BIOS and other boot settings.
issues.recommendation: The Virtual Connect Use-BIOS boot setting will be automatically changed to not bootable in OneView.

issues.description: Profile "Profile1" Ethernet connection 11 does not have an associated network. This connection will not be migrated because OneView does not allow server profile connections without an assigned network.
issues.recommendation: To migrate the server profile connection, assign a network to this connection. If virtual MAC addresses are configured, assigning a network to this connection will preserve these addresses.

issues.description: The network "1Network" is disabled and will be enabled in the OneView configuration.
